:

1. "Čoveka* su pozvali da se javi na vreme." (The man was called to come on time.)
2. "On se zanimao za to kako čovek* može da se razvije." (He was interested in how a man can develop.)
3. "Svi smo čoveci*." (We are all humans.)
4. "On je zaštitnik čovečanstva*." (He is a protector of humanity.)
5. "Čovečanstvo* je izgubilo nadu." (Humanity has lost hope.)